column5: Oh yeah!  Dont get mod qued tonight drifter???
M2, have you ever seen a guy able to drink that much Ale in 1 sitting? What a pair you two hooligans make! Looks like a great time.

Honestly I have no idea? I had 3 beers, I think he had the same and a plate of food. He had to be back at camp early.  That pic is about a week and a half ago. Brian is back at home now for his days off.  Hes a hoot to be around though! No shortage of good discussions thats for sure!
